v0.0.1

Changes since latest beta:

 * Choose GPLv3 as license. First public release
 * Engine totally rewrote to OpenGL. Now game should run faster and smoother ;)
 * New design and screen resolution (800x600)
 * Pause menu (needs redesign so please wait here :) )
 * Speed optimizations
 * Full autotools support (Linux). Official Gentoo ebuild
 * Fix paths problems on GNU/Linux. Resources are now loading from PREFIX/share/arkilloid/*
 * Source tree cosmetics
 * Bugfixes
 
Next planned release: 0.0.2/0.1.0
